        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】GlocalMe UniCord 3 合 1 多功能 USB 線，，65W 快充 + 可 4G 上網 + 支援 Lightning</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/10/glocalme-unicord/parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=glocalme-unicord</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/10/glocalme-unicord/parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Glocalme]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GloCalMe UniCord]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286323</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>隨著科技日新月異的發展，充電線早已不只是連接裝置與電源的工具。GlocalMe 推出的 UniCord 被譽為全球首款 3 合 1 多功能 USB 充電線，支援 65W 快速充電，更可使用 4G Cloud SIM 為你連接網絡，其重量僅為 44g。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286327" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011020836-694x377.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011020836-694x377.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011020836.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支援 65W</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286331" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲使用 CloudSIM 技術，支援全球 4G 上網</p><p>UniCord 的最大賣點在於其獨具匠心的 3 合 1 設計。它能使用 USB-C、Lightning 和 USB-A ，兼容市面上絕大多數電子裝置。無論是智能手機、平板電腦、藍牙耳機，還是其他配件，UniCord 都能為用户提供穩定且高效的充電與數據傳輸服務，消除了攜帶多條充電線的困擾，讓出行更加便捷。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286330" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/glocalmeunicordworld.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲原生支援 USBC，使用轉接頭即可支援 Apple Lightning 及 USB-A</p><p>UniCord 因其出色的創新性和實用性，成功榮獲在 CES 2025 展會 Android Authority 的「突破獎」，象徵著它在充電線市場中開創了全新的方向。從設計上來看，UniCord 支援快速充電，亦可使用 Cloud SIM 連接 4G 網絡，一條線就可充電、連接網絡，大大提升了專業人士在創作和工作的便利。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286328" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021232-694x376.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021232-694x376.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021232.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286329" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021227-694x383.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="383" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021227-694x383.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011021227.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286335" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104528-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104528-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104528.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286336" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104530-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104530-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104530.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>據官方網站數據顯示，GloCalMe UniCord 售價為 29.99 美元（約港幣 233.37 元），購買時可獲贈送全球 1GB 90 日數據服務，價值 29 美元（約港幣 225.66 元）。</p><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://www.glocalme.com/product/unicord/?gad_source=1&amp;gclid=CjwKCAiAhP67BhAVEiwA2E_9g8wiUbSgdGBCPjA5nIlWA_kxw5D5c4r8r0bjXQGLfS_j186eyPmnehoC7jEQAvD_BwE">GlocalMe</a>、Unwire.hk</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
