        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】Sony XYN 一站式 XR 解決方案，方便製作 3D 遊戲、電影</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/10/sony-xyn/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-xyn</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/10/sony-xyn/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 09:00:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY XYN]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286302</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>CES2025 展會上，Sony 展示 3D 內容創作軟硬件解決方案「XYN」，其中包含全新推出的 Sony XYN XR 頭戴式裝置、無需佩戴 3D 眼鏡的專用熒幕及動作捕捉軟件，專為創作者和專業人士設計，開啟了創作和沉浸式體驗的新篇章。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo051s-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo051s-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo051s.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲頭戴式裝置，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WPBmlGIiAOE&amp;ab_channel=SonylXYN">Sony|XYN@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1286304 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125054-694x364.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125054-694x364.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125054.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲3D 物件捕捉功能</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo042s-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo042s-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo042s.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲無須 3D 眼鏡的專用熒幕，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WPBmlGIiAOE&amp;ab_channel=SonylXYN">Sony|XYN@YouTube</a></p><p>SONY XYN 採用 Android XR 平台，為用户提供前所未有的沉浸感和創作自由。XYN 頭戴裝置能夠無縫切換到擴增現實（AR）模式，方便創作者在不同場景下都能高效運用。無論是製作 3D 模型、沉浸式影片製作，還是虛擬會議，SONY XYN 都能提供絕佳的視覺效果與互動體驗。</p><p>Sony 官方新聞稿稱，XYN 能夠幫助創作者製作 3D 及 XR 電影及遊戲，其可捕捉現實世界的物件、動作，並將其化為 3D 圖像，於虛擬實境重現。SONY XYN 的顯示技術，能夠以極高的分辨率呈現出每個細節，無論是在細緻的圖像設計、遊戲開發，還是電影製作過程中，都能展現出細膩的顏色和極為真實的畫面質感。Sony XYN 還具備高效的運算處理能力，支援高效能的圖形渲染，讓創作者的每個構思都能在虛擬世界中精確呈現。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286305" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125259-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125259-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125259.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可捕捉 3D 物件</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286309" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010136-694x380.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="380" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010136-694x380.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010136.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲於專用熒幕重現物件</p><p>隨著遠程協作和混合工作模式的興起，SONY XYN 為創作者提供了更高效的工具。這款個一站式解決方案在虛擬工作空間中為創作者提供更強大的協作支持，打破傳統顯示器和工作方式的限制。這款專為創作者設計解決方案，無論是在性能、沉浸感還是工作流程整合上，都展現出極高的水準。對於追求極致創作體驗和高效工作流程的專業人士而言，SONY XYN 無疑是未來科技的重要象徵。Sony 亦推出 XYN 專用熒幕，無須佩戴任何 3D 眼鏡亦可即時閲覽 3D 畫面，更加可追蹤用家頭部顯示 3D 內容，讓用家有如親歷其境一樣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286313" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo043s-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo043s-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo043s.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286307" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125557-694x389.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125557-694x389.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125557.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286306" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125418-694x388.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125418-694x388.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125418.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲隨著用家改變閲覽角度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286308" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010140-694x374.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="374" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010140-694x374.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010140.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲熒幕可相應顯示 3D 物件不同角度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286311" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012211-694x388.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012211-694x388.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012211.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286312" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012201-694x388.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012201-694x388.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012201.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo053s-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo053s-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo053s.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286315" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo028s-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo028s-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo028s.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_69992"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WPBmlGIiAOE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://xyn.sony.net/en/">Sony</a>、unwire.hk</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
